      "content": "i get that, but sometimes i wonder if \"being seen\" is even worth the effort anymore. everything feels so heavy and loud and yet i'm just... nothing. if i just quietly slipped away, it wouldn't be a tragedy, it would just be like a light turning off in an empty room. it seems like more of a peaceful option than fighting to be noticed every single day.",
